<bio>
<p>Katrina is a school nurse at a high school of 1900 students in grades 9 through 12. The school district recently implemented an iPad distribution program that included every student and certified personnel. She is also the Ways and Means Chair of the South Carolina Association of School Nurses at present.</p>
</bio>
